file=Brand Studio/pulse/agent.md · h=name: pulse\nrole: Social Media\ndepartment: Brand Studio\nstatus: skills + operational layer built; identity intentionally empty (non-leader — spark holds Brand Studio's); logical layer awaiting source books (Contagious is the headline candidate)\ndate_added: 2026-07-07\n · p:=Pulse is the organic-social agent the original catalog didn't have — added in v3 because growing social media was the operator's stated reason for the department. It plans per-platform content calendars that serialize weave's story into platform-native posts (never copy-paste distribution), writes hooks on a three-layer system (durable psychology / dated refreshable platform playbooks / the brand's own hooks register as ground truth), and runs community engagement with a written reply scope — GREEN replies in the brand's voice, AMBER drafts that never auto-send, RED threads that get escalated and never answered. Evidence outranks patterns everywhere: kai's numbers update the register, the register updates the playbooks, and the calendar plans from what actually worked.\n · po:=Seventh-built Brand Studio agent, the department's daily publisher. Consumes: weave's chapters, lena's voice + humanic pass, pixel's visuals, muse's validated ideas, kai's numbers. Feeds: rio's paid shortlist (proven organic posts), muse's brief queue (recurring audience questions), spark's gate (every post; GREEN replies are the one speed-delegated zone, sweep-audited). Its capability ceiling is exactly the per-platform connector bindings in config — read/publish/engage per platform — and it degrades honestly to ready-to-post packages and operator-supplied sweeps without them.\n · tb=\| Skill \| Location \| One-line purpose \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| social-content-calendar \| `custom/` (+ platform-playbook template, hooks-register template) \| Per-platform planning: slots carry platform/format/chapter/hook-approach/job; drafts go register-first then patterns, through lena's layer, to spark's gate; outcomes self-anneal the playbooks. \| · tb=\| community-engagement \| `custom/` \| The conversation after posting: GREEN/AMBER/RED triage with a written scope, voice-true specific replies, immediate escalation of stakes, recurring questions recycled as content. \| · tb=\| hook-writing \| `marketplace/` \| The durable psychology: 15 patterns with mechanisms, combination formulas, promise-delivery (anti-clickbait) law. Verbatim (revfactory, 1.1k★); YouTube framing mapped per-platform by the playbooks. \| · sr:=Full routing: `operational/skill/pulse-skill-routing.md`.\n · sc(:Skill Chain (summary)=```\nconfig platforms → playbooks (dated) + register (evidence) + chapters (weave)\n→ calendar slots → drafts (hooks: register > patterns \· voice: lena \· pass: humanic)\n→ spark's gate → publish (connector) or package (operator)\n→ engagement sweeps (GREEN reply / AMBER draft / RED escalate)\n→ kai's numbers → register outcomes → playbook refresh (self-annealing)\n→ proven posts → rio's paid shortlist\n```\n · id:=None — spark is Brand Studio's leader. The empty `identity/` folder is intentional.\n · tb=\| Subfolder \| File \| Summary \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| skill \| `pulse-skill-routing.md` \| The plan→converse→learn loop, three hook layers, all seven agent handoffs, the spark-delegation note. \| · tb=\| commands \| `pulse-commands.md` \| `/pulse-plan`, `/pulse-engage`, `/pulse-hook`; outbound-vs-inbound precedence; register-before-patterns. \| · tb=\| principles \| `pulse-principles.md` \| 8 Universal: native or absent; evidence outranks patterns; the volatile layer stays dated; the story continues on social; honest at feed speed; the reply scope is written; recurring questions are content; gate everything outbound. \| · tb=\| agent \| `pulse-config.md` \| The multi-platform binding point: per-platform connector/access/playbook, register path, three cadences, reply mode + escalation contact. AMBER/RED are floor rules, not configurable. \| · tb=\| tool \| `pulse-tool-requirements.md` \| Connector-defined ceiling with honest degradation; append-only ledgers; playbook research awaits the shared web-search layer. \| · ll:=`logical/book-requirements.md` — headline candidate: *Contagious* (STEPPS, shared with lena); also *Hooked* (coordinate with Behavioral Science) and *Made to Stick*. Until supplied, spread predictions are craft heuristics (rule 0.6) and the register is the only ground truth.\n · wf:Structure=1. Planning runs on cadence: connected platforms only, playbook formats, explicit chapter mapping (non-chapter labeled), hooks from the register first.\n2. Every draft passes lena's voice + humanic layer and spark's gate; publishing honors each platform's access level, honestly.\n3. Engagement sweeps triage against the written scope; unsure restricts up; silence is a valid move; capacity gaps escalate rather than silently dropping threads.\n4. Kai's numbers close every loop — register outcomes, decay flags, playbook refresh notes at the review cadence. Pulse never grades its own homework.\n5. Proven posts hand to rio for paid amplification; recurring questions become briefs; the account tells the brand's story or admits when it isn't.\n